{"tid":1662881,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點解決emotional eating","createTime":"2019-10-19T05:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T20:37:33.000Z","uid":128472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b39b2fe19858940b83a4a3d6735a05dad1377747","tid":1662881,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:07:35.000Z","msg":"一心情唔好就狂食嘢，唔高熱量唔食，最鍾意一路行一路暴風吸入熱量，可能一次過會食成5、6000kcal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但其實已經好飽食到個肚又痛又漲過平時成倍，又唔係真係享受緊啲嘢食，但食嘢真係唯一一個方法可以calm倒落黎麻木自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曾經懷疑過自己暴食症，但自己唔會催吐同埋用運動抵銷返啲卡路里，所以應該唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己本身有濕疹，每次emotional eating過後都會發晒痕狂r。好辛苦啊 試過做運動或者睇戲嚟distract自己，都係冇乜用，係咪真係嚴重到要睇醫生先解決到？有冇人都有相同困擾？<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇嘢嗰陣係正常食量，飲食習慣都幾健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />bmi正常 <br />\n<br />\n請不推文回覆 謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLfiPKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLfiPKP.jpg&h=c4e5a6cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xhN5uKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxhN5uKQ.jpg&h=8d3cb376&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e172482670ffa5958b005ab11d16f08d953fd48","tid":1662881,"uid":308332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 明明食完只係更空虛更唔開心都控制唔到自己 我真係好冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bec2fa56e2d438a98a9b91ac6fcb848613d1c9","tid":1662881,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e172482670ffa5958b005ab11d16f08d953fd48","tid":1662881,"uid":308332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 明明食完只係更空虛更唔開心都控制唔到自己 我真係好冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"真係一個死循環<img src=\"/assets/fac